    "synopsis": "The July 2018 issue of Shueisha's V Jump magazine revealed that the Dragon Ball Heroes game series will get a promotional anime this summer. The anime will depict the story's \"Prison Planet\" arc from Super Dragon Ball Heroes: Universe Mission. The anime's \"first episode\" will get an advance screening at the \"Super Dragon Ball Heroes Universe Tour 2018\" tournament event for the game at Aeon Lake Town in Saitama prefecture on July 1.\n\n(Source: Anime News Network)",
